          <td>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ol type=A>
            <a name="doc_1"></a>
            <li><a href="files/pbj_manual_1924.pdf">Instruckce k &#353;ifrov&#233;mu stoji 'Condenser PBJ'</a><br />
Instructions for Cipher Machine Condenser PBJ (in Czech language) <s><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="For Official Use Only">FOUO</span></s> <a href="#ref_3">[3]</a>.
            <div class="grey">
Note that the drawing in the original manual contains a mistake.
It shows 11 windows instead of 10.
            </div>
          </ol type=A>
        </font></td></tr></table>
