            <a name="lit_1"></a>
            <li><a href="files/Condenser_PBJ.pdf">The Condenser PBJ cipher machine</a><br />
Eugen Antal, Paul Reuvers, Pavol Zajac.<br />
Cryptologia. Forthcoming publication. Author's copy.
